{"tid":349924,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"【hkbuComm】歡迎加入浸大傳理！新生註冊日提示","createTime":"2017-08-07T01:25:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-08T13:10:27.000Z","uid":133889,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a7ee285bbd3d91dd18a09b3375894a4c16c22b47","tid":349924,"uid":133889,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T01:25:37.000Z","msg":"各位傳理新生：&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n歡迎你們成為傳理的一份子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n本年度香港浸會大學新生註冊日將於<strong>9/8（星期三）及10/8（星期四）</strong>舉行。&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n當日流程如下：<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/06/192526_7001885f172f7ea4fe9a98362c10557f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F06%2F192526_7001885f172f7ea4fe9a98362c10557f.jpg&h=2e2d16a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有意註冊成為傳理學會會員的同學，請帶備<strong>身份證丶原子筆和足夠現金（約$1500）</strong>回校辦理註冊手續。&nbsp;（＊當天傳理學會工作人員將身穿<span style=\"color: teal;\">粉綠底</span><span style=\"color: red;\">紅字</span>學會T恤，新生請跟隨工作人員指示完成整個註冊程序，以免走失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。）&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n另外，傳理學會迎新營（O&rsquo;Camp）將於<strong>19-21/8（星期六至一）</strong>&nbsp;舉行，有興趣的同學可於新生註冊日即場報名參加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n如欲了解更多迎新營資訊，可到以下連結觀看本年度迎新營宣傳短片： <br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KnbUTIXUOjc&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKnbUTIXUOjc%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=DWHvdOTzsFEJLSLEGP%2BqUZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=f0c39a9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KnbUTIXUOjc&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\n迎新營是展開大學生活的第一步，將會是你作為傳理人一生難忘的回憶。請不要猶豫，立即把握機會報名參加迎新營<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n等候成績覆核的同學，如結果公佈為入讀傳理，請即時聯絡我們！如有任何疑問，歡迎隨時聯絡 Woody（5161 5919）。&nbsp;大家亦可密切留意本會Facebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkbuCommSoc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FhkbuCommSoc%2F&d=DWHvdOTzsFEJLSLEGP%2BqUZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=7cd2008a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkbuCommSoc/</a><br />\n<br />\n最後，再次歡迎大家加入傳理大家庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n期待在新生註冊日與大家見面！&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n香港浸會大學傳理學會"},{"pid":"6bd2b46e7dc86f5f1d9f080feda724076c682ee3","tid":349924,"uid":133889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T01:31:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4a1923e87e2547f9244d4449d058718a79776b7","tid":349924,"uid":133889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T01:32:10.000Z","msg":"有咩問題都可以喺度問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd12472c39aad7dc86d3ef634731b9817b4646d3","tid":349924,"uid":133889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T01:41:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edfd7c501291cef871ff026523f33b8b1d1ed308","tid":349924,"uid":133889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T01:41:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df006ad5cbcd4439c6ce9de1c5164381175c4e47","tid":349924,"uid":133889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T01:51:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f518ffde07c54c82fe5636c7c7c33f5afa4330b","